flowchart TD
    Request[/GET /admin/customer<br/>bpNo, userId/] --> Controller[AdminController.getCustomer]
    Controller --> ServiceCall[adminService.getCustomer<br/>bpNo, userId]
    ServiceCall --> CheckParams{bpNo and userId<br/>both provided?}
    CheckParams -->|missing params| Resp400[/400 Bad Request/]
    CheckParams -->|valid| InvokeSAP[Call SAP CustomerDetailsRetrieval]
    InvokeSAP --> SAPEndpoint[SAP API<br/>/CustomerDetailsRetrieval]
    SAPEndpoint --> SAPResult{SAP response<br/>status?}
    SAPResult -->|error response| Resp5xx[/5xx Error Response/]
    SAPResult -->|success| CustomerType{Customer<br/>type?}
    CustomerType -->|MSSL customer| MSSLCall[Call SAP MSSLCustomerDetailsRetrieval]
    CustomerType -->|EBS customer| ProfileCall[Call SAP CustomerProfileRetrieval]
    MSSLCall --> MSSLEndpoint[SAP API<br/>/MSSLCustomerDetailsRetrieval]
    ProfileCall --> ProfileEndpoint[SAP API<br/>/CustomerProfileRetrieval]
    MSSLEndpoint --> FetchUser[Fetch user by userId]
    ProfileEndpoint --> FetchUser
    FetchUser --> UserStore[(External: Users DB)]
    UserStore --> UserFound{User<br/>found?}
    UserFound -->|not found| Resp404[/404 User Not Found/]
    UserFound -->|found| MaskData[Apply MaskingUtil<br/>to sensitive fields]
    MaskData --> Aggregate[Build GetCustomerResponse<br/>SAP data + user data]
    Aggregate --> Resp200[/200 GetCustomerResponse JSON/]
